targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  sub_q.days as "time",
  (sub_q.days - sub_q.dob) * 86400 as "Age in Secs",
  sub_q.name
FROM (
  SELECT 
    dob,
    name,
    generate_series(
          dob, 
          CURRENT_DATE, '1 week'
      )::date as "days"
  FROM maus_web_mouse
  WHERE
    -- name in ($m_name)
    deceased_on is NULL
) sub_q
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(dob)
ORDER BY 1

  sub_q.days as "time",
  sub_q.days - sub_q.dob as "Age in Days",
  sub_q.name
FROM (
  SELECT 
    dob,
    name,
    generate_series(
          dob, 
          CURRENT_DATE, '1 week'
      )::date as "days"
  FROM maus_web_mouse
  WHERE
    -- name in ($m_name)
    deceased_on is NULL
) sub_q
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(dob)
ORDER BY 1

SELECT
	  subq.age
FROM (
	SELECT 
		dob,
		name,
		CURRENT_DATE - dob as age
	FROM maus_web_mouse
) subq
WHERE
	$__timeFilter(dob)
AND subq.name in ($mouse)
